1
00:01:03,690 --> 00:01:05,900
[Elegy of ZhaoLi]

2
00:01:06,160 --> 00:01:09,750
[Episode 18]

3
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:39,820
Are you here to kill me?

4
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,710
Ms. Jiang,

5
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:54,560
I'm here to rescue you.

6
00:01:57,640 --> 00:02:00,300
What game are you playing now,
Prince Nianzhao?

7
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:03,320
Ms. Jiang, I really am here to save you.

8
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:04,510
Let's go quickly,

9
00:02:04,590 --> 00:02:05,840
or it will be too late.

10
00:02:08,910 --> 00:02:10,470
The entire palace now

11
00:02:10,470 --> 00:02:12,560
is under your control.

12
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,630
And I

13
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:16,520
am just someone abandoned by your brother.

14
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:19,310
You don't need to pretend

15
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:21,190
to be nice in front of me.

16
00:02:22,030 --> 00:02:23,120
Ms. Jiang,

17
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,870
all of this

18
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:27,000
was forced upon me by Mother.

19
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:29,680
I'm just a puppet with no choice.

20
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,079
While Jiuzhao was away from the palace,

21
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:33,190
Mother conspired with others

22
00:02:33,190 --> 00:02:34,680
to seize control of the court.

23
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:36,240
Now even those around me

24
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,310
are all spies placed by her.

25
00:02:38,710 --> 00:02:39,840
That's why earlier

26
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:42,760
I had no choice but to treat you that way.

27
00:02:42,910 --> 00:02:43,680
Ms. Jiang,

28
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,470
please believe me.

29
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,800
In this world,

30
00:02:47,190 --> 00:02:49,240
I'm the last person
who would harm Jiuzhao

31
00:02:49,240 --> 00:02:50,750
or the person he loves.

32
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:54,910
What...

33
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,640
What are you laughing at?

34
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,360
Prince Nianzhao,

35
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,360
stop pretending.

36
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:05,310
I know your secret.

37
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,520
You and Xun Simo

38
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:12,120
are both children of
the Empress Dowager and Old General Xun.

39
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:16,840
Ms. Jiang,

40
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:19,210
what are you talking about?

41
00:03:19,310 --> 00:03:19,910
I'm...

42
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:20,680
I found

43
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:23,030
the letter the late Emperor
left for my mother.

44
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:24,990
It clearly reveals

45
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:27,030
your true identity.

46
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:43,800
Yes.

47
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,430
So,

48
00:03:48,190 --> 00:03:51,280
what will it take for you
to hand over that letter?

49
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,750
Make me your Empress.

50
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:09,680
You wouldn't even
be Xie Jiuzhao's Empress.

51
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,400
Do you really think

52
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,360
I would believe you?

53
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:17,310
Xie Jiuzhao abandoned me and left.

54
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:19,120
He thought it was for my own good.

55
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,240
But what happened?

56
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:23,480
I ended up in your hands.

57
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:26,920
To survive, I can only rely on myself.

58
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:30,120
I'm so tired.

59
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,120
Now

60
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:37,310
I only want absolute power,

61
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:40,370
so no one can manipulate me again.

62
00:04:49,070 --> 00:04:51,390
Fine. Come with me.

63
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:13,680
You're not expecting me
to sleep here, are you?

64
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,430
It's not your first time here.

65
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,240
Besides,

66
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,600
if you want to be the Empress,

67
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:23,950
there are certain things

68
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:26,920
you'll have to do sooner or later.

69
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,000
So, Your Majesty,

70
00:05:32,950 --> 00:05:34,750
what do you want me to do?

71
00:05:38,190 --> 00:05:39,680
I'm not Xie Jiuzhao.

72
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:42,630
I have no interest in you.

73
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,330
You'll sleep here tonight.

74
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:46,920
If you dare to run,

75
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,950
I'll take your life.

76
00:05:51,430 --> 00:05:53,310
Are you leaving already?

77
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:57,120
What's wrong? Are you afraid of me?

78
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,950
You only have one letter in your hand,

79
00:06:02,950 --> 00:06:04,950
and I don't know if it's genuine.

80
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,560
Do you really think

81
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,680
I would be afraid of you?

82
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,510
I'm in your hands.

83
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,070
If that letter is fake,

84
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,600
just kill me then.

85
00:06:23,630 --> 00:06:24,680
Prince Nianzhao,

86
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,750
When Xie Jiuzhao confined me,

87
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:30,040
he at least let me
visit the study to pass the time.

88
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:32,100
Tomorrow I'd like to read some books.

89
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:36,000
You can't be stingier
than your brother, can you?

90
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:37,830
As you wish.

91
00:06:39,600 --> 00:06:40,800
Is everything arranged around?

92
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,390
Your Majesty,

93
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:43,120
everything has been arranged.

94
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:43,680
Go.

95
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,680
Find Xie Jiuzhao for me.

96
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:46,310
Yes.

97
00:06:48,970 --> 00:06:53,480
[Two days ago]

98
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,380
By order of the new Emperor:

99
00:06:59,380 --> 00:07:03,640
Apprehend the traitor Xie Jiuzhao
and return him to the palace for judgment!

100
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:08,270
I've only been away from
the palace for a few days,

101
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:11,530
and someone already dares to call
himself the new emperor?

102
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:16,630
Zhao.

103
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,390
Zhao!

104
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:26,680
Sir,

105
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,720
did you see that gentleman just now?

106
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:30,680
I think he went that way.

107
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,480
Thank you.

108
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,310
Zhao!

109
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,270
Li.

110
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:29,040
Are you trying to leave me behind again

111
00:08:29,040 --> 00:08:30,360
and face danger alone?

112
00:08:31,720 --> 00:08:32,270
No.

113
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:33,150
Xie Jiuzhao!

114
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,840
Do you see me

115
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:36,870
as a selfish woman

116
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:39,030
who's afraid of death?

117
00:08:39,150 --> 00:08:40,440
I said I would stay with you,

118
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,200
and that's not negotiable.

119
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,320
Even if it's perilous,

120
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:46,720
I'll accompany you even to the underworld!

121
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:49,010
But you made decisions on your own,

122
00:08:49,150 --> 00:08:50,510
leaving me behind.

123
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:52,170
You even tried to send me away!

124
00:08:52,390 --> 00:08:53,000
Li.

125
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,660
You thought it was for my good!

126
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,320
But do you know

127
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:59,620
how I felt

128
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:01,440
when you suddenly disappeared?

129
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,150
Li, I'm sorry.

130
00:09:06,630 --> 00:09:08,160
I'll never leave you again.

131
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,390
Then promise me

132
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:32,080
you'll never abandon me again.

133
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:35,910
I promise.

134
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,510
Who are they?

135
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:48,240
Miss Jiang,

136
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:50,510
Prince Nianzhao allied with
Ling's Army to seize the palace.

137
00:09:50,510 --> 00:09:51,750
We pretended to surrender

138
00:09:51,750 --> 00:09:52,870
and infiltrated the rebel forces.

139
00:09:52,870 --> 00:09:54,480
Today we were ordered
to capture His Majesty,

140
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,440
which gave us the chance
to leave the palace and meet you.

141
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,670
Prince Nianzhao?

142
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:59,080
How could he...

143
00:09:59,080 --> 00:09:59,870
Li,

144
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:01,870
the situation is urgent now.

145
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,870
I need troops to fight against them.

146
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:05,080
In the Imperial Study,

147
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:05,620
there's a secret passage
built by my father.

148
00:10:05,620 --> 00:10:07,160
[Imperial Study]

149
00:10:07,210 --> 00:10:09,000
But the mechanism
is also in the Imperial Study.

150
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:10,400
Someone needs to open it.

151
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,320
I'll go back to negotiate with them

152
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,600
and then open the passage
to bring troops into the palace.

153
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:17,440
This is our only chance of survival.

154
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,790
No, it's too dangerous.

155
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,600
If you go there,

156
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:23,470
they'll have no more restraints

157
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:27,030
and will definitely kill you first.

158
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:30,030
Since they were ordered to capture you,

159
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:31,630
why not let them take me back instead?

160
00:10:31,630 --> 00:10:33,630
I'll find a chance to open
the secret passage in the study for you.

161
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:34,320
Li,

162
00:10:34,790 --> 00:10:36,920
I can't let you put yourself in danger.

163
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:38,870
I'll be fine, Zhao.

164
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:42,480
They're exposed while you can hide.

165
00:10:42,790 --> 00:10:43,790
If I go,

166
00:10:43,870 --> 00:10:45,550
Xie Nianzhao will only try every means

167
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:47,000
to use me to draw you out.

168
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,240
No.

169
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:52,200
Zhao, don't worry.

170
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:54,240
I have my own plan.

171
00:11:08,750 --> 00:11:10,000
Ms. Jiang.
